{"id":77804,"title":"How to address the communication needs of older patients with hearing loss.","abstract":"Hearing loss is a common problem in older people and may have a negative effect on their care while in hospital, as well as resulting in significant cost to the NHS. This article outlines the findings of a two-year project in an NHS trust to improve the care of older people with hearing loss. An important outcome of the project was the development of a hearing loss toolkit containing good practice recommendations and tools to help staff in all NHS trusts, and other care settings, implement practical and cost-effective improvements. ","date":"2014-06-30","categories":"Otorhinolaryngologic Diseases","split":"test","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24975079","annotations":[{"name":"Old age","weight":0.509281,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Old_age"},{"name":"Communication","weight":0.45775,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Communication"},{"name":"Hospital","weight":0.233777,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hospital"},{"name":"Trust law","weight":0.214722,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Trust_law"},{"name":"Hearing impairment","weight":0.0617798,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hearing_impairment"},{"name":"National Health Service","weight":0.034968,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/National_Health_Service"},{"name":"NHS trust","weight":0.0329831,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/NHS_trust"},{"name":"Urban planning","weight":0.0318009,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Urban_planning"},{"name":"Negative liberty","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Negative_liberty"},{"name":"List of toolkits","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_toolkits"},{"name":"Hearing (sense)","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hearing_(sense)"},